style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I wanted to take the time =
to thank you very much for meeting with Chris, David and myself at your =
place this afternoon. It was much =
appreciated.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I felt that the meeting =
was very productive and positive as we all discussed the next steps and =
have agreed on the claim=E2=80=99s progression process moving =
forward.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I would like to re-confirm =
the next steps we agreed to in writing, and share with all as =
below:</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><ol =
start=3D"1" type=3D"1" style=3D"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: =
0in;"><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">Asset Restore to attend site as soon as possible and complete the =
process of assessing and cataloging the contents for the response of the =
contents claim. After assessment the contents which are categorised as a =
total loss will be removed from site.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; =
font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Asset =
Restore to strip out the property of any fire or smoke damaged linings =
or other non-structural items. This will enable a clear and clean =
structural assessment to be undertaken, from which we will produce a =
scope of works for the repairs required.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; =
font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Once =
we have a scope of works completed =E2=80=93 we will share this with you =
to approve before we submit to our repair panel for =
tendering.</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol><div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Confirming that you have =
notified us of the access code to be =
1106.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">We will keep you updated on the above process =
and communicate with you as we move through the above =
steps.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I have spoken with both =
our Motor and our Claims Team Leaders, and they have said that the items =
you have enquired about are very unlikely to be affected by the fire =
given their location with respect to the proximity of the fire. I do =
understand that you would like to be 100% certain that the lithium =
batteries in these items have not been affected from the fire. The =
standard process in this situation is that you can undertake any testing =
of any of your items which you wish to, to obtain test results or a =
report which your insurer can consider for inclusion in your claims. If =
the test results prove any damage or loss to these items from the fire =
=E2=80=93 then your insurer will consider them within your =
claim.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">For contents items - =
please direct your enquiries to<span =
class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a =
href=3D"mailto:claims@tower.co.nz" style=3D"color: blue; =
text-decoration: underline;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(70, 120, =
134);">claims@tower.co.nz</span></a></span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><d=
iv><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">As you do not yet have a =
motor claim with Tower from this event =E2=80=93 you can also send any =
motor reports to<a href=3D"mailto:claims@tower.co.nz" style=3D"color: =
blue; text-decoration: underline;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(70, 120, =
134);">claims@tower.co.nz</span></a><span =
class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and they will respond =
accordingly.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Thank you again and I =
strongly encourage you to call me on the number below with any concerns =
that you have with the process of the claim =
progression.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">All the =
best,</span><o:p></o:p></div></div></div><div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Grant.<span =
class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><o:p></o:p></div></div=
></div><table class=3D"MsoNormalTable" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" =
cellpadding=3D"0" style=3D"border-collapse: collapse;"><tbody><tr =
style=3D"height: 126.75pt;"><td width=3D"243" style=3D"width: 182.25pt; =
